Description
msvc.exceptions
Contains classes related to the 32-bit exception handling data structures created by Microsoft Visual C++.
  • Classes in msvc.exceptions used by msvc.exceptions

    Description
    BlockType
    Enumerates the two types of blocks used in C++ exception handling.
